                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-sergeant D</hi> 5.) I heard Eade say the bag was thrown over the wall—I went and got it—I showed it to Mrs. Montague, who identified it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was running to Astley's theatre; I never saw the bag.</p>
